These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-1::.
There 7 different types of food: eggplant, cucumber, peas, pomegranate, watermelon, grapes, papaya
There are 7 different nationalities: canadian, italian, indian, british, egyptian, indonesian, australian
 1. the person eating peas is on the far left##1
 2. the person eating pomegranate is not the indonesian##6
 3. the canadian is on the left of the person eating cucumber##1
 4. the australian is somewhere to the right of the egyptian##5
 5. the person eating watermelon is on the left or right of the person eating papaya##3
 6. the canadian is on the right of the person eating peas##1
 7. the person eating grapes is somewhere between the person eating cucumber and the italian##7
 8. the italian is on the left of the australian##1
 9. the british is somewhere between the person eating watermelon and the indian##7
10. the indian is on the left or right of the canadian##3
11. the egyptian is on the far left##1
12. the person eating pomegranate is somewhere to the left of the australian##5
13. the person eating pomegranate is somewhere to the right of the person eating grapes##5
14. the person eating papaya is somewhere to the right of the person eating watermelon##5
15. the person eating watermelon is the italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4     |     5     |     6     |    7    |
| Food          | peas    | eggplant    | cucumber | grapes | pomegranate | watermelon    | papaya |
| Nationality   | egyptian | canadian | indian  | indonesian   | british    | italian | australian |

