.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-2::.
There 7 different types of food: corn, onion, eggplant, carrot, mango, papaya, pineapple
The people have 7 different hobbies: magic-tricks, dancing, traveling, cooking, baking, woodworking, puzzles
 1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere between the person eating pineapple and the person eating onion##7
 2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the person eating carrot##1
 3. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
 5. the person eating corn is somewhere between the person who's hobby is cooking and the person who's hobby is dancing##7
 6. the person eating papaya is somewhere between the person eating carrot and the person who's hobby is traveling##7
 7. the person eating mango is somewhere between the person eating carrot and the person eating onion##7
 8. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 9. the person who's hobby is baking is somewhere to the left of the person eating mango##5
10. the person eating mango is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##5
11. the person who's hobby is woodworking is not the person eating pineapple##6
12. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
13. the person who's hobby is baking is between the person who's hobby is cooking and the person eating carrot##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |       5       |      6      |    7    |
| Food    | pineapple  | eggplant | papaya | carrot | corn     | mango | onion  |
| Hobby   | traveling | woodworking | dancing  | puzzles  | baking | cooking      | magic-tricks |

