 7. the person who's sport is climbing is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##5
 8. the person driving the taxi is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 9. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere to the right of the person driving the skateboard##5
10. the person driving the car is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
11. the person who's sport is surfing is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##5
12. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is climbing##3
13. the person driving the airplane is somewhere between the person who's sport is biathlon and the person driving the motorbike##7
14. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person driving the bus##1
15. the person driving the car is the person who's sport is soccer##1
